sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor R as Retail (Redeemer)
    participant X as REXPrimary<br/>(Sepolia)
    participant O as NavOracle<br/>(Sepolia)
    participant K as Keeper<br/>(off-chain)
    participant H as Hyperlane<br/>Bridge
    participant E as PruvExecutor<br/>(PRUV)
    participant P as Pruv RWAToken<br/>(PRUV)

    Note over R,X: PHASE 1 - Request
    R->>X: requestRedeem(wRWA)
    X->>X: khoá wRWA vào redeem-queue, cấp receipt
    Note over R,X: cancelRequest được trước khi epoch chốt (ERC-7887)

    Note over X,P: PHASE 2 - Epoch initiate
    K->>X: initiateEpoch()
    X->>O: nav()
    O-->>X: NAV
    X->>X: matching @ NAV (match P2P trước)
    X->>H: bridge NET wRWA sang PRUV
    X->>X: epoch = in-flight

    Note over H,P: PHASE 3 - Redeem ở PRUV (async)
    H-->>E: giao wRWA (relay)
    E->>P: redeem(wRWA, executor, executor)
    P-->>E: USDC
    E->>H: bridge USDC về Sepolia

    Note over X,R: PHASE 4 - Settle + phân phối
    H-->>X: giao USDC (relay)
    K->>X: settleEpoch()
    X->>X: phân phối USDC cho redeemer theo NAV
    R->>X: claim(receipt)
    X-->>R: USDC
